title: respect of the area to which the following Order relates, hereby order as follows:
heading: 3. The area consisting of the Local Electoral Area of Tullow is prescribed
text_raw:
3. The area consisting of the Local Electoral Area of Tullow is prescribed 
as a rent pressure zone during the period commencing on 15 May 2025 and 
ending on 31 December 2025. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

13 May, 2025. 

JAMES BROWNE, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 16th May, 2025.

heading: (This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal
text_raw:
EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation) 

This Order provides for the designation of the Local Electoral Area of Tullow as 
a rent pressure zone under section 24A of the Residential Tenancies Act 2004 
(as inserted by section 36 of the Planning and Development (Housing) and 
Residential Tenancies Act 2016), for the period commencing on 15 May 2025 
and ending on 31 December 2025.
